Text like "READY" in Megaman games is sprites (or some small words on this fashion). Everything else is BG, simply because sprites are too much limited on NES to do any text with.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=38">Bregalad</a> — Fri Jun 16, 2006 9:57 am</p><hr />
